<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-21 13:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8710 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-FURNITURE-DELIVERY-BO     07-21 0740
