<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-21 15:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8865 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k BC-TEENS-JOBS-HNS &LR;      07-21 0688
