   COXNET WHEELS 0718 -- Although the 2000 Isuzu Rodeo is a quite
civilized sport-utility vehicle, it will issue reminders that Isuzu
is a truck manufacturer and not a carmaker. The ride is noticeably
trucklike, and not even Isuzu's Intelligent Suspension Control
system (ISC) prevents that. (DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
