who'll play a cunning vixen this fall on NBC's deliciously campy
soap Titans, says casting directors have her pegged all wrong. ``I
don't know why it took people this long to get it,'' Bleeth says.
In fact, Bleeth admits she's quite the naughty girl. She certainly
looked that way during her chat with a roomful of TV reporters.
Fall TV Tour from Los Angeles. (Thompson, Palm Beach Post).
