issue with a segment from ABC-TV's ``20/20'' by correspondent John
Stossel that attempted to debunk the movie ``Erin Brockovich'' by
claiming there's no proof that exposure to hexavalent chromium can
make you sick. By Dana Bartholomew. (Will move in the ``a''
