   SALMON (Undated) - U.S. Rep. Matt Salmon has formed a foundation
to push issues like education and child welfare at the Arizona
Capitol, but many see it as a prelude to his expected bid for
governor in 2002. The Foundation for Arizona's Future, which Salmon
