<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-21 19:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9123 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-FASHION-FLATTERY-NYT &LR;      07-21 1223
