<HEADLINE>
WAXING ELOQUENT ON CD BURNERS
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 By DR. EMILIO BOMBAY 
 c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Dear Dr. Bombay: I bought a CD writer to make CDs from our 600
LPs. I am able to get the records to play through the computer
