<DOCNO> NYT20000721.0318 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-21 20:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9277 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r a BC-WACO-REPORT-TEX     07-21 1241
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WACO-REPORT-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DANFORTH INVESTIGATION ABSOLVES GOVERNMENT IN DAVIDIAN SEIGE
</HEADLINE>
  (Resending to fix byline) 
 (For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
 By DIANNA HUNT 
 And TONI HEINZL 
 c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ST. LOUIS _ A 10-month, $11 million investigation into the
standoff and final inferno near Waco in 1993 has cleared the
