<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: in 6th graf, updates with U.S., Russian officials meeting
Saturday; adds new 15th-17th grafs on Clinton's early departure,
Mori meeting
 &HT;    U.S. EXPRESSES INTEREST, CONFUSION IN DEAL TO END NORTH KOREAN
MISSILE TESTS
